<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>根；根茎；词根；根源：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the roots of a tree 
树根</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Words often come from the same root. 
词常常有相同的词根。</p><footer>人教② – 2</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Money is often said to be <strong>the root of all evil</strong>. 
金钱常被说成是万恶之源。</p></div></div>